{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回\"坐怀不乱\"讲述了楚留香被石观音掳至其宫殿后的惊险对峙。石观音以绝世容颜和暧昧姿态诱惑楚留香，试图征服这位名满天下的风流侠客。然而楚留香不为所动，以\"坐怀不乱\"的定力三次拒绝石观音的勾引：先将她抛出，再泼酒于她身上，最后直言揭露她征服男人后又将其贬为奴仆的病态心理。石观音恼羞成怒，提起曾拒绝她的\"石驼\"的悲惨下场相威胁，楚留香却冷静指出石驼早已逃脱。石观音最终暴怒将楚留香赶出。楚留香假装中迷香实则早已清醒，此时展露真力，将押送他的两名侍女击倒，与姬冰雁、一点红汇合。三人互相扶持准备逃离，楚留香又闯入浴室盘问沐浴的侍女苏蓉蓉等人的下落，得知她们并不在此处。一点红牵挂曲姑娘安危，曲姑娘却突然出现冷言讥讽。胡铁花则在沙漠中艰难挣扎，濒临绝境。本章展现了楚留香面对致命诱惑时的过人意志和智谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叹息的只怕别人说我吹牛。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吹牛?……我一向对别人说的话都很了解，但这句话，我却实在不懂。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "日后若有人问起我：'可见过石夫人?'我自然说见过，那人若再问我：'石夫人长得是何模样?'我可就回答不出了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "那人见我忽然语拙，必定要认为我是吹牛，却不知夫人容貌之美，世上本无一人能够形容。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我平生也听过不少恭维话，却从来也没像这样能令我开心的了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你许久以前就听到过我的名字，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但直到现在，你才见到我的真面目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你失望么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "夫人看我可像失望的模样?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你不觉我老?",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "对女人说来，'老'确是最可怕的敌人，但夫人显然已将这可怕的敌人征服了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知道这里是什么地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "除了夫人的闺房外，世上哪里还有这样的所在?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知我为何要你来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既知道，为何还不过来?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论今后会怎样，有了今夜，你就永远也不会后悔了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我从来都不会后悔的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "瞧你的神情，好像以为我是个疯子，是么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你难道不是疯子?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我只恨现在没有力气，将你抛得更远些。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你忍心么?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是个很有经验的男人，是么?",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么你就该知道，我现在是多么需要你，你忍心拒绝我么?",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这里已是天堂，你还等什么?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "不错，美人的躯体，的确就是男人的天堂……只可惜这天堂却离地狱太近了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "现在你更要认为我是疯子了，是么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不是疯，你只不过是个白痴而已。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "你认为一个正常的人，是绝对无法拒绝你的，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "永远也不能的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "那些山谷中的奴隶，也许就是因为太正常了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你说什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我若不拒绝你，就也会和他们一样，去扫那永远也扫不尽的风沙，直到死去为止，因为你见到一个特殊的男人，就想征服他，占有他，要他将灵魂都奉献给你，但等到这男人真的将一切都奉献给你时，你便又会觉得这男人太卑贱，最多也不过只配为你去扫地。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "也许这因为你的心灵很空虚，所以一直在不停地寻找，想找个男人来填补这空虚，但你却永远也找不到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "也许我所要找的男人就是你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "现在你或许觉得我和别的男人都有些不同，但等到我也被你征服时，也就会和他们一样了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你对你自己难道没有一点自信?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我不是没有自信，只不过不愿意冒这个险而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我……我难道还不值得你冒险?",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "也许我觉得世上还没有一个女人值得我为她冒生命之险的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "苏蓉蓉呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "在我眼中，她们并不是女人，只不过是我的好朋友，为了自己好朋友，大多数男人都会冒生命之险的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你不知道，拒绝我的男人会有什么结果么?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "除了我之外，难道还有别的男人拒绝过你?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "有一个，许多年前曾经有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知道我对他怎么了?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "你杀了他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "杀了他，哪有如此容易……我将他赤裸裸地放在烈日下，让烈日晒毁他的脸，晒瞎他的眼睛，再让他像骡子般推磨，永久也不许他有片刻休息……",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知道他最后变成了什么模样?",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你难道也想变成他那副模样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我只知道他并没有死，他后来终于逃了出去，我也知道他现在虽然痛苦，但也比那些扫地的人好得多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你……你永远也休想活着逃出去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "我还知道，你现在对我还没有完全死心，还不会像那样折磨我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "石观音",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "滚!趁我还没有杀死你之前，快滚出去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shi_guan_yin",
      "text": "遵命!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "我走不动了，姑娘来扶我一扶好么?",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "前面就到，这两步路你难道都不能走?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘难道如此狠心，要我爬过去吗?",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "另一少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "大少爷，求求你，别替我们找麻烦行不行，已经有两个人为你送了命，一个人为你断了手，你还不满意?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ling_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "但现在……我只求姑娘们扶我两步……否则我只好坐下来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真是个魔星，女人见到你，真是倒楣。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "看来你对那位石夫人，倒真是卖力得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "想不到你的想像力也如此丰富，只可惜你却想错了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抱歉得很，在下虽不愿恩将仇报，但为了逃命，这也是没法子的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你哪里来的力气?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "好像是天生的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但……但那迷香……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你当我真的也和你们一样，也被那见鬼的迷香迷晕过去了么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，你自然是假装的，否则你又怎会比我们先晕过去，又比我们后醒过来?但石观音没回来时，你为何不逃走?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "那时我还想见她一面哩!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "现在我已将那位石观音气疯了，一个半时辰内，她绝不会出来，咱们要走，就得趁这个时候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但我们还是没有力气，只怕走不出去。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你先将红兄背在背上，用这腰带扎紧，我再背起你……你站起来的力气总该有吧?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘们请放心，在下等都是正人君子，眼睛绝不会胡乱看的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正人君子为何……为何不许人家穿衣服?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "这只因在下知道，一个人身子若是赤裸着时，就不大会说谎的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "而且也一定不好意思出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "现在我只想请问姑娘，石夫人将苏蓉蓉、李红袖和宋甜儿三个人藏在什么地方了?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "三个人?是男的还是女的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "自然是女的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我们夫人从来不会将女人藏起来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_yi_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "另一少女",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这里一共有五十六位姐妹，但都没有姓苏的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你看她们说的可是真话?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "女人在如此情况下，还能说谎的并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "如此说来，她们的确是不在这里的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_mu_yu_shao_nv",
      "text": "沙漠上每天渴死的人至少有十个，姑娘们却在这里洗澡……唉!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认得出去的路么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "她们将我抬进来时，我已记住了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "蓉儿既不在这里，你为何还不快走?这里的女子武功都不弱，你若遇见几个穿着衣服的，只怕就麻烦了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想找个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "莫非是那位曲姑娘?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只觉得不能让她留在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "但你认为她会跟咱们走么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕不会的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你既明知她不会跟咱们走，为何还要去找她?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却知道，她至少不会阻拦咱们……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "曲姑娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你凭什么以为她不会拦阻你?就凭你们三人这样子，若能逃得出去，这地方只怕早已变成了一片瓦砾。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    }
  ],
